Loqui -- IRC/Chat client for Gtk2
=================================

What's this?
------------
Loqui is an IRC/Chat client for a Gtk2 environment.

Features
--------
 - Supports multiple servers.
 - Supports multiple protocols (IRC, IP Messenger (Experimental)).
 - The common buffer (a buffer to show messages on the channels that not currently selected).

How to install?
---------------
See INSTALL.

